item.title: Dedicated to my mother: Srikanth Nadhamuni
item.description: Dedicated to my mother: Srikanth Nadhamuni Mysuru: Speaking to Star of Mysore this morning, Srikanth Nadhamuni, co-founder of 10-Bed-ICU, said the programme consists of 10-Bed-ICU equipment donation, COVID Management Technology Platform and a Doctor Connect programme.
